{
  "stem": "24268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I later on tried to close my eyes and to put this on-- on this little paper, which came out perfect, by the way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I could never do this again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was blonde.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she had the braids taken in front-- very attractive, with the gray jacket, made out of blanket-- who knows what.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she had a brown skirt, I think, pleated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was-- you know, she was the one who was in charge of this camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Beside what and above her was the German SS women, also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But she was-- she was a witch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She wanted-- matter of fact, she wanted to liquidate the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was already rumored.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They started-- they took, I think, 170 girls for the death march, which I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They took 170 girls out of our concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I don't-- God know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then, the last minute, the [NON-ENGLISH] said-- yeah, Branca Weinstock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She went to the SS woman and pleaded with her to leave us in camp, because the end was so close, obviously, that she persuade her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she did-- left us in camp, [? without ?] evacuation anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that's why we remain in Peterswaldau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Peterswaldau-- I just said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they left us there, without moving-- nowhere, with the liquation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, we wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "May the 5th, the Russian marched in and they liberated us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they Hungar-- I told you about the lady who I met from Hungary, Hungarian lady?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her husband was a district doctor-- matter of fact-- from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When she-- when the war got ended, they sent Red Cross special buses to pick up their citizens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she asked me to come with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, Rosika-- she called me Rosika.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
